      "text": "Un Jehkabs zehlahs Rih-\ntā agri / un nehme to Akmini/\nkas tam bij Pagalwē bijis / un\nuszhle to par weenu Sihmi/ un\nuslehje tam Etji wirfu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nosauze tahs Weetas\nWahrdu Betete/ bet papreeffch\nbija tam Pilsfahtam Lus Wahr-\ndā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs apfohlida-\nmees apfohlijahs/ un fazzija: Ja\nDeews ar mannim buhs / un\nmann paſargahs ue scho Zeltu/\nko es staigaju / un dohs man\nMaisi ehst / un Drehbes ap-\ngehrbtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un liks mann ar Meeru\npahreet/manna Tehwa Nammā/\nTad buhs tam KUNGAM man\npar Deewu buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un schim Akminain/ ko es\npar weennu Sihmi efimu uszehlis/\nbuhs par weennu Deewa-Nammu\ntapt/ un wiffu/ ko tu man doh-\nſt/ no ta dohſchu es tew to def-\nmitu Teefu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXIX. Nodalla.\nJehkabs fastohp Raëlu ar tahm Awim : 6.\nDsirdina Lahbana Awis / un stuhpsta Ra-\nëli/ fazzidams jewieſſam Rebekkas Dehlu: 11.\nKalpo Raëles pehz ſeptix Saddus : 16. Bet\nLea tohp winnam Raëles Weeta pewesta : 23.\nVar to barrahs wiꞥſch ar jawu Tehwotsi Lab-\nhanu : 25. Tas dohd winnam Raëli arri,\ndsan : 28. Rubbens / Sihmeans / Lewis /\nJuha/ peedsemm no Leas : 31.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N Jehkabs mettahs\nkahjop / un gahje us to\nRaushu Semini / kas\nprett Rihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſtattijahs/ un redſi/ tur nija tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "bija Akka wirs Lauka : Un r\ngi / tur bija trihs Awju-P\npee tahs paschas/ jo no tahs\nkas tappe tahs Awis dsirdit\nun weens leels Akmins bija u\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tahs Akkas Zauruma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur patt tappe t\nAwju-Pulki fadsihți/ nn tee\nwehle to Akmini no tahs A\nZauruma/ un dsirdtja tahs A\nun likke atkah to Akmini us\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Affas Zaurumu jawā Weet\nTad fazzija Jehkabs\nteem: Manni Brahti / no\nrenes juhs effat? un tee faz\nmehs effam no Abranas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us te\nPasihstat juhs Lahbanu N\nDehlu? un tee fazzija : mel\ngan pasihftam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch\nteem: Arrig tam labbi klahj\nun tee atbildeja ; gann labbi\nreds/ Raële wiꞥſch Meita/ te\nar Awim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: R\nSaule irr wehl augsta/ weh\nka newaid Lohpus pahrd\ndsirdijeet tahs Awis/un eit\npagannijeet tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee: Me\nwarram/ pirns wiſſi Awju-\nſi fadsihți tohp/ ka tee to\nni no Akkas Zauruma nowe\nmehs tahs Awis dsirdijain\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad wiꞥſch wehl ar\nrunnaja / tad nahze Raë-\ntahm Awim / kas wiṅṅas\nwam peederreja / jo wiṅṅa\n"
    }
